lking is Bogus - Introducing Buggies\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003eThey scurry, they fight, and now—they help you survive. Hatch, raise, and ride your own insect friends - buggies! Saddle up and ride through the park, command them in battle, or have them help gather resources. The right partner could mean the difference between thriving and barely surviving.  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003cspan class=\"bb_img_ctn\"\u003e\u003cvideo class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/6a3f1e2962e2d15a040f30f9c92ad895.poster.avif?t=1784045614\" width=1170 height=658 \u003e\u003csource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/6a3f1e2962e2d15a040f30f9c92ad895.webm?t=1784045614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"\u003e\u003csource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/6a3f1e2962e2d15a040f30f9c92ad895.mp4?t=1784045614\" type=\"video/mp4\"\u003e\u003c/video\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBig Baddies of the Park\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e The park is home to creatures other than the bugs you know and love. AXL, the tarantula, and the Lizard stand as apex predators that demand preparation, strategy, and courage. The snake is a different kind of challenge. To master it, you will need to learn its patterns, ride it, and harvest its scales. And let\u0027s not forget about the bird. Every encounter makes you stronger. Claim rare materials, craft powerful gear, and unlock upgrades that push you further into a world built to overwhelm you.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003cspan class=\"bb_img_ctn\"\u003e\u003cvideo class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/aa752c57c7558c2b9f2252964bb6d0a1.poster.avif?t=1784045614\" width=1170 height=658 \u003e\u003csource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/aa752c57c7558c2b9f2252964bb6d0a1.webm?t=1784045614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"\u003e\u003csource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/aa752c57c7558c2b9f2252964bb6d0a1.mp4?t=1784045614\" type=\"video/mp4\"\u003e\u003c/video\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePlaygrounds\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003eSurvival is only the beginning. With Playgrounds, you can build your own challenges using powerful tools that shape combat, puzzles, and unpredictable encounters. Download, play, and vote on community creations to discover new ways to test your skills. The park is no longer just a place to survive. It is a place to create.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003cspan class=\"bb_img_ctn\"\u003e\u003cvideo class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/0e0af5bff5d6486960c182c0ea4ae9c7.poster.avif?t=1784045614\" width=1170 height=658 \u003e\u003csource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/0e0af5bff5d6486960c182c0ea4ae9c7.webm?t=1784045614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"\u003e\u003csource src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661300/extras/0e0af5bff5d6486960c182c0ea4ae9c7.mp4?t=1784045614\" type=\"video/mp4\"\u003e\u003c/video\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eA Shadow That Follows You\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/u\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"bb_paragraph\" \u003eThe threat is always there—watching, learning, waiting. You don’t know where it’s coming from, only that it never leaves. The deeper you dig, the closer it gets. Some mysteries should stay buried, but it’s too late now. It knows you’re looking. And it’s ready. Every answer drags you deeper, every step invites something closer. You were never alone. You thought you were in control. You were wrong.\u003c/p\u003e",
